<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your Tax Situation Deserves a Plan</title>
    <style>
      body,
      table,
      td,
      p,
      a {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      body {
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      img {
        border: 0;
        display: block;
        outline: none;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        padding: 30px 0;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #1a2744;
        padding: 30px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-header img {
        max-width: 200px;
        height: auto;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .hero-banner {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2744 0%, #2c4a7c 100%);
        padding: 28px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .hero-banner h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.3;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .hero-banner p {
        color: #b8c9e0;
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 36px 40px;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .email-body p {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #444444;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1a2744;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .highlight-box {
        background-color: #f0f5fb;
        border-left: 4px solid #2c4a7c;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 20px 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .highlight-box p {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .highlight-box p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .highlight-box strong {
        color: #1a2744;
      }
      .cta-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #2c4a7c;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 36px;
        border-radius: 6px;
      }
      .divider {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #e8ecf1;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .step-item {
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #444;
      }
      .email-footer {
        background-color: #1a2744;
        padding: 28px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-footer p {
        color: #8fa3bf;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .email-footer a {
        color: #b8c9e0;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .footer-phone {
        font-size: 16px !important;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-bottom: 12px !important;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
        .email-body,
        .email-header,
        .hero-banner,
        .email-footer {
          padding-left: 24px !important;
          padding-right: 24px !important;
        }
        .hero-banner h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <table
        class="email-container"
        role="presentation"
        cellpadding="0"
        cellspacing="0"
        width="100%"
      >
        <tr><td class="email-header"><img
              src="cid:emailLogo"
              alt="Wynn Tax Solutions"
            /></td></tr>
        <tr><td class="hero-banner">
            <h1>Every Tax Situation Is Different &mdash;<br />Yours Deserves a
              Real Plan</h1>
            <p>Here's what a consultation with our team looks like</p>
          </td></tr>
        <tr><td class="email-body">
            <p class="greeting">Hi {{name}},</p>
            <p>We know that dealing with tax issues can feel overwhelming,
              especially when you're not sure where to start. That's exactly why
              our team begins every client relationship the same way &mdash;
              with a thorough, no-pressure consultation designed around
              <em>your</em>
              specific circumstances.</p>
            <p>No two tax situations are alike. Whether you're navigating a
              balance with the IRS, sorting out years of unfiled returns, or
              simply trying to understand a notice you received, our approach
              starts with listening &mdash; not selling.</p>
            <div class="highlight-box">
              <p><strong>What happens during your consultation:</strong></p>
              <p>&#10003; A senior consultant reviews your situation in detail</p>
              <p>&#10003; We identify which IRS or state programs may apply to
                you</p>
              <p>&#10003; You receive a clear explanation of your options
                &mdash; no jargon</p>
              <p>&#10003; We outline a recommended path forward with realistic
                timelines</p>
              <p>&#10003; All of your questions are answered before any
                commitment</p>
            </div>
            <p>Our consultations are complimentary and completely confidential.
              There's no obligation, and many clients tell us that just having a
              clear picture of where they stand brings immediate peace of mind.</p>
            <hr class="divider" />
            <p
              style="font-weight:600; color:#1a2744; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:16px;"
            >Why clients choose Wynn Tax Solutions</p>
            <div class="step-item">&#128101;
              <strong>Personalized attention</strong>
              &mdash; You'll work with a dedicated consultant who knows your
              file inside and out.</div>
            <div class="step-item">&#128200;
              <strong>Proven strategies</strong>
              &mdash; We build resolution plans based on years of experience
              with IRS and state agencies.</div>
            <div class="step-item">&#128274;
              <strong>Full transparency</strong>
              &mdash; You'll always know where your case stands, what's next,
              and why.</div>
            <p>Ready to get a clear picture of your options? Let's set up a time
              to talk.</p>
            <div class="cta-wrapper"><a
                href="{{scheduleUrl}}"
                class="cta-button"
              >Book Your Free Consultation</a></div>
            <p style="text-align:center; font-size:14px; color:#666;">Or call us
              toll-free:
              <strong style="color:#1a2744;">{{phone}}</strong></p>
            <hr class="divider" />
            <p style="font-size:13px; color:#888; line-height:1.6;">You're
              receiving this email because you recently expressed interest in
              Wynn Tax Solutions. If you'd prefer not to receive follow-ups,
              simply reply and let us know.</p>
          </td></tr>
        <tr><td class="email-footer">
            <p class="footer-phone">&#128222; {{phone}}</p>
            <p><strong style="color:#fff;">Wynn Tax Solutions</strong></p>
            <p>Tax Resolution &amp; Relief Services</p>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;"><a
                href="https://www.wynntaxsolutions.com"
              >wynntaxsolutions.com</a></p>
            <p style="margin-top:14px; font-size:11px; color:#6b829e;">&copy;
              {{year}}
              Wynn Tax Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>
          </td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>